## Formatting

We can add sample sizes for the  overall stats on people who wear glasses using the `pattern = ` argument:

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
inline_text(table1, variable = "glasses", column = "stat_0",
            pattern = "{n}/{N} ({p}%)")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
3,894/8450 (46%)
```


:::
:::


