## Readability

Because this can be hard to read, I'd suggest storing those stats in a chunk before the text:

````
```{{r}}
glasses_f <- inline_text(table1, variable = "glasses", 
                         column = "stat_2")
glasses_m <- inline_text(table1, variable = "glasses", 
                         column = "stat_1")
